Armed Militias Loyal to Gbagbo Target Non-Indigneous People in Ivory Coast

-- B y   P a u l i n e   B a x
-- 
2011-02-28T19:52:04Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-28/armed-militias-loyal-to-gbagbo-target-non-indigneous-people-in-ivory-coast.html
     Feb 28 (Bloomberg) - Armed militias loyal toÂ incumbent
President  Laurent Gbagbo  are targeting non-indigenous citizens
in  Ivory Coast , according to the rival government of Alassane
Ouattara.  A Muslim man was burned alive by militias over the weekend,
and two Togolese citizens were killed by militias, according to
military spokesman Captain Leon Alla in a statement sent to
Bloomberg News.  Both incidents happened in the commercial capital Abidjan,
the statement said. Six others had been killed by militias in
the interior of the country, the statement said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
